WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:04.466
Hey, my ex-husband and my father-in-law are dead

2
00:00:04.466 --> 00:00:07.033
My ex-husband has a sick sister

3
00:00:07.333 --> 00:00:10.433
I kindly stayed and took care of him

4
00:00:10.566 --> 00:00:14.300
I didn't expect the villagers to say that I cut off my palm

5
00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:16.666
pass it on

6
00:00:16.733 --> 00:00:19.066
I know it for ten miles

7
00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:22.366
Hey, I didn't expect Sister Mei's experience to be so miserable.

8
00:00:22.366 --> 00:00:24.400
What is Xiao Zhang doing in Zhoujiazhuang?

9
00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:26.100
I was sent by the Municipal People's Hospital for an internship.

10
00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:27.166
Three months as a teacher

11
00:00:27.766 --> 00:00:29.466
Oh, no wonder.

12
00:00:29.466 --> 00:00:30.700
I went to the health station yesterday.

13
00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:33.666
I heard from Dr. Zhou that a handsome guy will come to help

14
00:00:33.966 --> 00:00:35.500
So here's the thing.

15
00:00:35.866 --> 00:00:37.100
Not only the handsome guy

16
00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:38.633
Still a handsome guy

17
00:00:38.700 --> 00:00:39.833
Mei took it

18
00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:43.100
It's noon, why don't you come home with me for dinner first?

19
00:00:43.266 --> 00:00:45.500
I'll take you to the health post at 2pm

20
00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:48.266
Anyway, Zhou Yusheng is an old acquaintance with me

21
00:00:48.333 --> 00:00:49.200
Don't be afraid.

22
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:52.933
This is probably not very convenient, right? What's the inconvenience?

23
00:00:52.933 --> 00:00:54.066
Let's go!

24
00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:56.500
Still not suitable

25
00:00:56.500 --> 00:00:58.066
What's the inconvenience?

26
00:00:58.066 --> 00:01:00.700
Think about it, you saved my life

27
00:01:00.700 --> 00:01:01.766
If it weren't for you

28
00:01:01.766 --> 00:01:03.566
I could die on the street

29
00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:07.400
What's up?

